data.description: Discover the charm of lake view living in this cozy Bonney Lake gem! Nestled on a large, fully fenced lot with ample space for parking and a serene lake nearby!  This 2 bed/1 bath one-level home features an inviting open floor plan, laminate floors, newer windows, and a large farm sink in the kitchen!  The remodeled bathroom showcases a new vanity and tile floors. Large shed in backyard for storage! With easy access to Hwy 410 and walking distance to the boat launch and Ken Simmons Park, this quiet neighborhood offers the perfect blend of serenity and convenience.  Come see today!
